properties.rationale: Crisis Communication Protocol applies to Rackspace Customer Portal as a critical customer-facing system
Diversity and Inclusion Programs apply enterprise-wide including portal-based systems
Community Engagement Program Controls (Rackspace Foundation) apply to all enterprise systems including the Customer Portal
Service Deprecation Notice Process applies to Rackspace Customer Portal service lifecycle management
System Use Notification (AC-8) control applies to Rackspace Customer Portal as an internet-facing system
Social Media Governance Controls apply to Rackspace Customer Portal digital communications
Anti-Harassment Investigation Procedures apply to all Rackspace systems including the Customer Portal
Brand and Communications Governance Controls apply to the Rackspace Customer Portal as a customer-facing system
Travel and Expense Approval Controls apply to the Rackspace Customer Portal expense management workflows
Compensation and Benefits Administration Controls apply to Rackspace systems supporting HR processes
